WEBVTT

00:00:01.055 --> 00:00:03.279
Holding hands,

00:00:03.303 --> 00:00:05.146
we watched the door,

00:00:05.170 --> 00:00:08.359
boring holes in it
with our intense stares.

00:00:09.303 --> 00:00:14.052
My siblings and I were waiting for our mom
to come back from the hospital,

00:00:14.076 --> 00:00:18.249
where my grandmother was having surgery
for advanced cancer.

00:00:19.353 --> 00:00:21.319
Finally, the doors opened,

00:00:21.746 --> 00:00:23.046
and my mom said,

00:00:23.505 --> 00:00:25.469
"She didn't survive the operation."

